title: I AM ATHLETE | Aaron Donald: Rams Contract Uncertainty, Retirement and Donda Sports
description:
SUBSCRIBE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE?sub_confirmation=1

The 7x All-Pro and 3x NFL Defensive Player of the Year Aaron Donald joins Brandon Marshall, Pacman Jones and LeSean McCoy in episode 34 of I Am Athlete. Watch as AD talks L.A. Rams contract extension, a potential retirement and inking a new deal with Ye's Donda Sports.
